Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,資質
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,襲名 襲名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星? 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結晶化的雙晶素與你的靈魂產生共鳴並閃耀了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎已經退燒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…可以襲名了
